  05 Jul 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  17 Jun 2005; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Marked ppc stable.

  21 May 2005; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  stable on x86 and amd64

  12 May 2005; Eldad Zack <eldad@gentoo.org>
  +files/libvisual-0.2.0-movd.patch, libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Fixed assembler movd misuse. Patch provided by Nickolay Kolchin-Semyonov
  <nbkolchin@yandex.ru>. Closes Bug 86859.

  15 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.1.6.ebuild:
  dont make use of the pic useflag any longer

  06 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> +files/0.2.0-ppc.patch,
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  added patch to fix compilation on ppc, fixes bug #86533

*libvisual-0.2.0 (02 Mar 2005)

  02 Mar 2005; Gregorio Guidi <greg_g@gentoo.org> +libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
